query:
SELECT u.id as user_id, u.name as user_name, u.email as user_email, u.roleId, 
       e.id as employee_id, e.name as employee_name, e.email as employee_email, e.userId as linked_user_id
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN employees e ON e.userId = u.id
WHERE u.name LIKE '%سماح%' OR e.name LIKE '%سماح%';
